title: Pavel Macháček
text:
Pavel Macháček (born 18 December 1977) is a Czech <a href="association%20football">football</a> defender currently playing for <a href="FK%20Bohemians%20Prague%20%28St%C5%99%C3%AD%C5%BEkov%29">FK Bohemians Prague (Střížkov)</a> in the <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>.
Career statistics.
"Statistics accurate as of 30 June 2012"
